      <h2 class="subtitle is-2">
        80% of Americans own a Smart Phone
      </h2>
      <div class="content">
      	<p class="is-size-4"> The average smart phone probes the world for WiFi, anywhere from 800 to 2000 probe signals per hour. Constellation's suite of tools allows you to turn these signals into insight. How many phones enter your space, acts as a proxy for the number of people walking in the door.<p>

		<p class="is-size-4">Our services <strong>do not collect personal information on your customers</strong>, ensuring the utmost privacy. All you need to get started, is a WiFi enabled computer.<p>		

   	 
